<h1>Donations</h1>

<div class="block-text">
  <p>Any Rat Rescue relies on public support to keep their doors open to rats in need.<p>
</div>

<div class="button">
  <button type="button" class="donate"><%= link_to "Donate Now", "https://www.paypal.com/", target: "_blank" %></button>
</div>

